      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so quiet here. like, i go through the whole day, work my shift, eat, sleep, and it’s the same silence every single night. i feel like if i just stopped showing up to things, or if i just stopped being active online... would it even matter? it feels like i'm just a ghost in this apartment.",
